N catplot.pkg
D  4 Feb 2022
U 7
d 'CATPLOT': module for plots of frequencies, fractions or percents of categorical data
d 
d catplot shows frequencies (or optionally fractions or percents)
d of the categories of one, two or three categorical variables. The
d first named variable is innermost on the display; that is, its
d categories vary fastest. catplot is a wrapper for graph hbar
d (default) or graph bar or graph dot. The files catplot_old.* are
d files for the original 2003 version of catplot: to use fix the
d names by removing "_old".
d 
d KW: graphics
d KW: categorical data
d KW: bar charts
d KW: dot charts
d 
d Requires: Stata version 8.0
d 
d 
d Author: Nicholas J. Cox, Durham University
d Support: email  N.J.Cox@@durham.ac.uk
d 
d Distribution-Date: 20101221
d 
f c\catplot.ado
f c\catplot.hlp
f c\catplot_old.ado
f c\catplot_old.hlp
e
